data.description: ***Buyer lost financing so THIS may be YOUR opportunity to call this beautiful bungalow "home"..!  Set in a desirable Auburn neighborhood ~ this house was stripped to the studs and reconfigured in order to make way for a larger kitchen and an added bathroom!  All fixtures, finishes and appliances are brand-new. You'll also enjoy the benefits of a brand-new roof, windows, electrical and plumbing for years to come. Enjoy your morning coffee from your front-porch this Fall. You'll be toasty next winter thanks to all new insulation throughout the home and a brand-new Buderus boiler. Even your vehicles will be tucked away in the oversized, two-car garage complete with a work area. This property is minutes away from town amenities which include shopping and dining.. and just minutes to 290, 395, the Mass Pike and Route 20.
